summary:
Since 2010 I work as a technician in an IT consultancy. I also work in the art and entertainment industry as an event producer and musician manager. In the year 2020 I started working as a IT Support Analyst in an Argentina Fintech called REBA that give a beautiful experience that helped  to grow as a IT professional.
Thanks to my experience in the IT services sector, I learned to solve technical problems in any field, of different levels of difficulty and always willing to learn. Working as a team I was training until then.
But taking into account the development of my other activity as a producer in the management of shows, I can say that I am able to develop in several activities to solve problems. Learning I want to move forward and expand my work horizons.
Nowadays I'm living in The Netherlands looking for and opportunity as Technician in an International Firm.
